## Backend local dev example
# Copy to `backend/.env.local` and fill values.
# (This repo ignores `.env.local` so secrets won't be committed.)

# OAuth (local dev). Prefer GF_* keys to avoid clashing with firebase-tools auto-loading backend/.env
GF_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=...
GF_GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=...

# Frontend base URL (can include path, e.g. https://example.com/gformgen/)
GF_FRONTEND_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# Optional: lock down CORS (comma-separated). Default is "*".
GF_CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173

# Required: fixed OAuth redirect URI. Must exactly match Google OAuth client settings.
# Local dev example:
GF_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URI=http://localhost:3000/auth/google/callback


